*qingy-1.0.0-r1 (26 Jan 2014)

  26 Jan 2014; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +qingy-1.0.0-r1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml, qingy-1.0.0.ebuild:
  qingy-1.0.0: fix bug #359637 Updating sys-apps/qingy-1.0.0 autotools files:
  thanks to Justin for reporting, hal and axs for testing, Justin and s4t4n for
  fixing. Fix bug #462634 - sys-apps/qingy-1.0.0 build error: Thanks to Ole
  Langbehn for reporting, Rafal Muzylo, Ellison Marks, needle and Stephan
  Litterst for help. qingy-1.0.0-r1: Fix bug #372675 - sys-apps/qingy fails to
  keep ConsoleKit PAM session open with default setting (using DirectFB: Thanks
  to guboj for reporting, Richard Kenney for testing, Tomoh K. and s4t4n for
  fixing. Patches are from qingy upstream subversion.

  27 May 2013; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> files/50qingy-gentoo.el:
  Autoload correct function in Emacs site-init file, bug 392029.

